      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle that gets the job done? This car is a solid choice for anyone seeking reliable transportation at a great value! While it shows some visible signs of age and regular use, it remains a functional and steady performer ready for the road. It's the perfect opportunity to own a hardworking vehicle that still has plenty of life left in it!",
