    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading in the clear coat, and minor dings on the door panels. Inside, the upholstery has visible wear and some staining, though all essential features and electronics remain functional. It has been maintained mechanically to keep it running safely, but a buyer should expect the aesthetic and tactile signs of a well-used car.",
