    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a donor for parts. The engine is currently running very poorly and will require a comprehensive mechanical overhaul to be roadworthy again. Externally, the body shows significant signs of age, including noticeable rust patches, faded paint, and several dents. The interior is also heavily worn, with torn upholstery and some missing trim pieces. While it is not currently in driving condition, it offers a solid foundation for someone with the tools and time to restore it.",
