      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, exhibiting a flawless aesthetic and mechanical profile that mirrors its original showroom delivery. Every surface, from the refined interior appointments to the immaculate exterior finish, reflects a legacy of fastidious preservation. For the discerning driver who demands perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly superlative condition.",
